data.description: Welcome to 1820 S 7th Street, a fantastic duplex with oversized garage nestled in the heart of East Passyunk in South Philadelphia! Located in a vibrant and sought-after neighborhood, 1820 S 7th Street enjoys the best of both worlds: the tranquility of a residential area and the proximity to urban amenities. From eclectic eateries and trendy boutiques along Passyunk Ave to cultural landmarks and green spaces, this location truly offers a balanced city living experience. Just steps away from the popular Bok Bar, walkable to the Broad Street Line, the Italian Market, and more.  This property presents a unique opportunity for both homeowners and investors, with one unit rented and another vacant, allowing for either owner occupancy or the option to generate additional income by renting the second unit. There are two generously sized units each containing one bedroom and one bathroom, with layouts that could allow the living rooms to be used as additional bedrooms and rented as two bedrooms. The units are in great condition and can be rented right away, or spruced up even more with light cosmetic upgrades to boost rents. The oversized garage, large enough for truck parking, could also generate additional income! Step onto the expansive bi-level roof deck and be captivated by breathtaking views of Center City Philadelphia. Whether you're entertaining guests or simply relaxing outdoors, this space offers a picturesque backdrop that's sure to impress.   Don't miss out on this chance to own a piece of Philadelphia's charm while capitalizing on the income potential of a duplex property. Schedule a viewing today!
